name: Elaine Starling
what_you_do: Elaine Starling is recognized for her video show and podcast, The Abundance Journey™. She created The Abundance Journey™ 6 week course to share what she learned from a conversation with a higher power during a stroke.
who_you_serve: Elaine mentors spiritual, growth-oriented women to align with Divine guidance to achieve their dreams.
offering: As the Abundance Ambassador, Elaine guides entrepreneurs and experts to turn problems into abundance with an Abundance Mindset.
social_proof: Elaine is an international TEDx speaker and bestselling author.
signature_programs: The Abundance Journey™ 6 week course, Activate Abundance
business_focus: Elaine helps entrepreneurs and experts get the most out of life and make a difference through her Abundance Journey program.
